-- GD Power Says Inner Mongolia Wind Farm Project Approved by United Nations
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-22T00:19:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/gd-power-says-inner-mongolia-wind-farm-project-approved-by-united-nations.html

          
          
             GD Power Development Co. said its
Inner Mongolia wind farm was approved as a Clean Development
Mechanism project by the United Nations.  
 The wind farm in the northern Chinese province, with
capacity of 49.5 megawatts, is capable of reducing carbon
dioxide emissions by 134,000 tons a year, GD Power said in a
statement on its website.  
          
          


  


        